dc:description: Colorless yellow.  Intact.  Black weathering on rim which has corroded in areas to show iridescence.  Strain cracking.  Fair material.  Blowing spirals and some pinprick bubbles.  Shallow bowl with bell shaped contour on a stem.  Hollow rim folded outward and downward.  Slanting impressions on base.  Pontil mark.
